    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power through a crisp G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis remains taut, utilizing a multi-link rear suspension geometry that excels in corner exit stability. Recent service includes a preventative IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh clutch assembly, ensuring powertrain integrity. The braking system employs four-piston Brembo monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors, providing exceptional thermal management and firm pedal feel. While the finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical fundamentals\u2014including the Variocam Plus timing and Bosch Motronic management\u2014are dialed in for immediate performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
